**Do you currently have security experience and looking for new job opportunities?**<br>
**Are you looking for a job close to home in the Melrose Park area?**<br>
**Seeking employment with a company that offers their employees incentives?**<br>
<br>
If you answered "Yes", then Black Knight Security wants you to join their team!<br>
<br>
APPLY TODAY by clicking on the link below:<br>
<a href="https://workforcenow.adp.com/jobs/apply/posting.html?client=blackknigh&amp;jobId=46840&amp;lang=en_US&amp;source=CC2" rel="nofollow">https://workforcenow.adp.com/jobs/apply/posting.html?client=blackknigh&amp;jobId=46840&amp;lang=en_US&amp;source=CC2</a><br>
 <br>
We are now hiring Security Officer for full-time and part-time positions.<br>
<br>
HIRING IMMEDIATELY for ALL SHIFTS (Overnight, 1st Shift and 2nd Shift)!<br>
<br>
Pay rate is $12.00 hour <br>
 <br>
Job Responsibilities:<br>
- Patrol premises to prevent and detect unwanted activity<br>
- Ensures safety and security of all building occupants and property<br>
- Protects property from theft, embezzlement, sabotage, fire, and accidents<br>
- Investigates and writes reports on incidents in a timely manner<br>
- Maintains professional demeanor and excellent service delivery<br>
- Utilize the emergency procedures to address any emergencies at a respective work site<br>
- De-escalate any violence within the given guidelines of a security officer's training<br>
- Perform as a team player to support co-workers, supervisors, and management<br>
- Perform other related duties as assigned by an account manager <br>
 <br>
Job Requirements:<br>
- Must have a current PERC card and 20 hours training certificate<br>
- Must have reliable transportation<br>
- Must have a clean criminal background<br>
- Candidates must pass a drug screen<br>
- Must be at least 21 years old<br>
- Intermediate computer skills<br>
- Steady work history with at least one former employer for a period of 2 years<br>
- High school diploma or GED<br>
- Must have the ability to speak, read, and write clearly in English<br>
- Must be eligible to work in the United States <br>
 <br>
There are many benefits to working on the Black Knight Security team:<br>
1. Great Compensation<br>
2. Medical and Dental Benefits (Full time only)<br>
3. Paid Vacation (Full time only)<br>
4. Holiday Pay<br>
3. Extra Work Hours Available<br>
4. Team-building Events<br>
5. Company Paid CPR/AED Training<br>
6. Bereavement Leave<br>
7. Advancement Opportunities!<br>
 <br>
APPLY TODAY!<br>
 <br>
EOE/Minorities/Females/Vet/Disability<br>
Black Knight Security is an Equal Opportunity Employer committed to hiring a diverse workforce.<br>
    </section>

